The paper proposes a machine learning model for Click Through Rate (CTR) prediction in online advertising system using user behavior images. This involves handling large amounts of images in one sample, which requires efficient distributed machine learning. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM).
